How to get .mp4 to play on PSP:

make sure you have a memory card!

Rename the files as M4V0000xx ((XX being the movie number such as 1 2 3 ect))

create a folder named MP_ROOT

Put all movies in x:\\MP_ROOT\100MNV01 (X being the drive your memory card is located)


(((there are programs you can download online to rename the file, just search google or here)))
